  <brief_title>Observational and Epidemiologic Study of the Disease Course and Unmet Needs in Children With Symptomatic Moderate to Severe Allergic Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 2-year Prospective, Multi-center, Observational and Epidemiologic Outcomes Study of the Disease Course and Unmet Needs in Children With Symptomatic Moderate to Severe Allergic Asthma</official_title>
